Work Summary
 StatsBomb Open Data
	 Retrieved the full StatsBomb Open Data ZIP from their official GitHub repo.
	 Unpacked the archive and organized datasets in local storagae.
	 Confirmed folder structure and checked availability of essential files:
	competitions.json → details of competitions & seasons
	 matches/ → match-level metadata
	 lineups/ → squad and player participation info
	 events/ → in-game actions (passes, shots, fouls, pressures, etc.)
	 three-sixty/ → freeze-frame player positioning
 Transfermarkt Data
	Downloaded player transfer datasets from Transfermarkt (ZIP format).
	Extracted files and placed them in local directories for preprocessing.
	Verified accessibility of all extracted files.

